h1 New Custom Policy Integration

p.help Integrate a custom policy into this admin portal. The JSON schema describes the form that will be rendered when configuring the policy in the APIcast configuration page for any of your APIs.


- content_for :javascripts do
  = javascript_pack_tag 'custom_policy'

= render 'errors'

= content_tag :div, class: 'PoliciesWidget', id: 'custom-policy-container', data: { policy: @policy.as_json } do end
